downloadTitle: Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 Reference: Tables and Table Groups
downloadDescription: This worksheet lists all core Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 data tables.
detailsSection: This spreadsheet includes the name, table group, table type, whether the table is a system table, whether the table is visible in the Application Object Tree (AOT), and whether the table is shared.
systemRequirementsSection: For information about the system requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012, see System requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click Download to download the document.
  2. Save the file to your computer.
